    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Hungarian Chamber (Vienna, 21 August 1551)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">Gáspár Zula presents quite a few things on Oláh’s
                            behalf, and he asks them to trust his words and make sure the gunners
                            and the military equipment are sent to Eger, lest they lack
                            anything.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Reverende Venerabilis et Egregii Domini et Fratres
                    Observandissimi!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Is magister <persName>Gaspar</persName> praepositus Landicensis<note
                        type="critic" xml:id="note.1">Gáspár Zula was a scribe at the Hungarian
                        Chancellery between 1548 and 1552, see <hi rend="smallcap">Fazekas</hi>
                        2021, 503. He received the Provostry of Lendak in 1548, thanks to
                        Oláh.</note> nonnulla meo nomine Dominationibus Vestris est relaturus. Rogo
                    igitur easdem, velint verbis ipsius fidem praestare et considerare, praesentis
                    temporis periculo magistros bombardarum fossionesque cum aliis instrumentibus
                        <placeName>Agriam</placeName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.2"
                        >Eger.</note> sine more expedire, ne quis <del corresp="Olahus">istic</del>
                    defectus contra opinionem <persName>maiestatis regiae</persName>, domini nostri
                    clementissimi et nostrum omnium istic contingat. Dominationes Vestras feliciter
                    valere opto, cui me commendo.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Ex <placeName>Wienna</placeName> 21. Augusti anno 1551.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">
                    <seg type="signature">Vester Agriensis etc. manu propria</seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.5">Reverendo venerabili ac egregiis dominis consiliariis camerae
                    Hungaricae sacratissimae maiestatis regiae etc. dominis et fratribus
                    observandissimis.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
